          "text": "Skilljar is better for customer education. It was purpose-built for external training with deep Salesforce integration, built-in monetization, content syndication, and certification with LinkedIn integration. Absorb can handle customer education through its eCommerce portal, but it's an extension of an employee training platform rather than a purpose-built solution."
